                            What is the impact of the pandemic on Ryerson’s budget?
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1597677061415-what-is-the-impact-of-the-pandemic-on-ryerson-s-budget-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1597677061415-what-is-the-impact-of-the-pandemic-on-ryerson-s-budget-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1597677061415 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="4949d776-a1e4-40cd-a436-d1a3c89be9d2" >

    <p>The university is incurring significant costs with approximately $10 million incurred by the end of April alone, less than two months into the pandemic. Within 2020-21, expenditures will include enhanced supports for students, IT costs, support for remote and online learning and teaching, and PPE for example.</p> 
<p>At the same time revenues are expected to decrease with lower enrolment. As we move into the Fall, we will be monitoring enrolment levels and the impact on university revenues.</p>
    





